{"tid":1087081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：令和證明日本蠻野不正的華夏藩屬本色","createTime":"2019-04-01T06:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T08:37:13.000Z","uid":17641,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d8f0aa75996fc280804c50af0409759b0388d905","tid":1087081,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:42:26.000Z","msg":"萬葉集》以漢字記錄日本古詩，詞序用日文語法，但此句則明顯是用華夏雅言書寫，前兩句仿照《禮記》筆法，有漢朝平和風格，後兩句卻有魏晉六朝綺麗萎靡之氣，承接《楚辭》蠻野不正之風，而且詞句之景物對仗生硬，在華夏詩禮之國屬於打油詩、科舉落第文人劣作之流。<br />\n日本好想脫離華夏，但選此詩句，卻是證明其蠻野不正的華夏藩屬本色。要脫華，不是這樣脫的。日本是脫衣的脫，不是脫胎的脫。"},{"pid":"d549ef149db7e8d72e5af6c483cf8ff05678289c","tid":1087081,"uid":35430,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:55:46.000Z","msg":"唔係打晒飛機話徐福帶三千童男童女過日本咩？<br />\n照計人地先係華夏正宗喎"},{"pid":"c21b85b6b7bd6bc93a11fea84aa9fc26ae54f194","tid":1087081,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:57:56.000Z","msg":"後兩句卻有魏晉六朝綺麗萎靡之氣，承接《楚辭》蠻野不正之風<br />\n<br />\n魏晉家陣又變左蠻野不正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cdc084c86b03c7cfcd04383b1a84b4e67ac6a7","tid":1087081,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:58:50.000Z","msg":"癡線佬食左藥未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大中華毒真係冇藥醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9fde48aa35e7e64fe075e4f6e87b2fd0fff0ac","tid":1087081,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T07:24:30.000Z","msg":"中原華夏文化即胡梵大雜燴文化"},{"pid":"1c82751d79fb208dea0d5423ed1aca8d7b6d368b","tid":1087081,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T08:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NHq2p7t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNHq2p7t.jpg&h=63f8dcc0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm